WEBVTT

00:00:31.385 --> 00:00:33.129
I address this letter

00:00:33.863 --> 00:00:35.644
simply to you,

00:00:36.494 --> 00:00:38.062
even though we both know

00:00:38.086 --> 00:00:42.228
there are many of you behind this "you,"

00:00:43.306 --> 00:00:47.024
and many of me behind this "I."

00:00:50.525 --> 00:00:53.081
I write to you because at present,

00:00:54.478 --> 00:00:58.799
this quaking world we share scares me.